    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影終わりの帰り道",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（連日撮影が続く中、渚は役のモデルが自分だと）\n（知ってから、さらに演技に磨きがかかっていた）",
      "startTime": 6.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（一応最後の撮影まで付き添う予定だが、明日は）\n（芽衣の撮影もあるんだよな。時間は大丈夫だったか……）",
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "今、私以外の子のこと考えてました？\n私が隣にいるのに……酷い……",
      "startTime": 23.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　あ、い、いや……\n一応、スケジュールの確認を、と思っただけで……",
      "startTime": 29.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ごめんなさい、深い意味はなくて……\nだ、ダメですね、どうも最近役が抜けなくて……",
      "startTime": 37.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんだそういうことだったのか……\nびっくりしたぞ……",
      "startTime": 47.0739990119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さらに数日後",
      "startTime": 49.5304294269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "今日の演技、どうでしたか？\nちゃんと見守ってくれていましたよね？",
      "startTime": 54.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "も……もちろん、ちゃんと見ていたよ\n誰にも文句を言わせない素晴らしい演技だったぞ",
      "startTime": 60.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……{user}さんのおかげです\n貴方がそばでずっと見てくれているから……",
      "startTime": 68.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "だからずっと私のこと見守っていて下さいね\n約束ですよ？　破らないで下さいね？",
      "startTime": 77.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（ライバル役のアリサちゃんが憑依してるぞ……渚……）\n（だが下手に突っ込んで演技に影響が出たら問題だ）",
      "startTime": 85.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（撮影が終わるまではこのままにしておこう……）\n（生きた心地がしないが）",
      "startTime": 93.0666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――渚の最終撮影日",
      "startTime": 95.8206761044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（今日でついに渚のクランクアップ……）\n（主人公達の結婚式に飛び込んでくるシーンだ）",
      "startTime": 100.9764097881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 104.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "おかしいよ、今日は私とコウタ君の結婚式でしょう！？\nどうしてその女と結ばれようとしてるのっ！！",
      "startTime": 110.7999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、どうしてっ、なんで！！\n貴方を幸せに出来るのは……！！",
      "startTime": 117.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "わ……私じゃ、なかったの……？\nユイナじゃないと、ダメ、なの……？",
      "startTime": 125.5333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "ぐすっ……分かっ、分かってたよ……ずっと！\nそんなの分かってた！！　だってコウタ君のこと……",
      "startTime": 136.6999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "私、なんでも知ってるもん……大好き、だから……\n幸せになってね……絶対だよ？　結婚、おめでとう……",
      "startTime": 154.2999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（渚が……ライバル役も素敵なキャラだと言った理由）\n（この台詞でなんとなく分かった気がするな……）",
      "startTime": 169.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "最後のシーンも一発OK、ですか……？\nあ、ありがとうございますっ！！",
      "startTime": 176.4333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "本当に凄い演技だったぞ、渚……\nそばで最後まで見れて良かったよ……ありがとう",
      "startTime": 182.6333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "お礼を言うのは私の方です\nずっと付き合ってくれてありがとうございました！",
      "startTime": 189.4666748047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（ああ、良かった……いつもの渚だ）\n（撮影が終わって、役も抜けきったようだな）",
      "startTime": 196.7666748047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これで終わりなんですねー……\nそっか……ちょっとだけ名残惜しいです",
      "startTime": 204.7666748047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、主人公達が鐘を鳴らすシーン\n私が言った通り、とっても素敵じゃなかったですか？",
      "startTime": 214.1333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "出来るなら、自分でも鳴らしてみたかったな～って……\nふふ、なんて、ファンの気持ちが出ちゃってますけど",
      "startTime": 224.3999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ原作が好きだったんだもんな\n……分かった、ちょっと待っててくれ",
      "startTime": 232.6999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
